                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-14T11:00:00-05:14">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 14, 1914, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Owing to revolutionary conditions Congress has granted extraordinary powers to
                    the President.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
